The Chartered Society of Physiotherapy (CSP) is the professional, educational and trade union body for the UK's 65,000 chartered physiotherapists, physiotherapy students and support workers.

Since 1999, the National Reigster of Personal Trainers (NRPT.co.uk) has been the 'go to' place as THE online directory. We have over 800 Qualified and Insured trainers nationwide. Our experienced personal trainer members work in gyms, PT studios, homes or local parks right across the country.
